e is on the board of directors at sothebys mr reza was previously employed as a managing directormergers  acquisitions by lazard freres  co llc transactions date shares transaction value     acquisition at  per share      acquisition at  per share      acquisition at  per share      acquisition at  per share      acquisition at  per share      acquisition at  per share      acquisition at  per share  copyright  factset research systems inc all rights reserved source factset fundamentals officers and executives mr thomas s smith president chief executive officer  director mr adam david chinn executive vice president  chief operating officer mr michael fenton goss chief financial officer  executive vp mr scott henry executive vptechnology  worldwide operations mr jan prasens managing directoreurope region mr jene a levine chief global compliance counsel  executive vp mr marc porter chairmanfine art division mr dennis m weibling director mr michael l gillis treasurer  senior vice president mr david goodman executive vpdigital development  marketing mr kevin m delaney chief accounting officer senior vp  controller mr vincent l montagnino senior vice president  directorworldwide taxes ms lauren e gioia executive vp  directorworldwide communications ms jennifer park headinvestor relations mr david g schwartz secretary  senior vice president mr jonathan a olsoff executive vice president  general counsel mr domenico de sole chairman mr peregrine andrew morny cavendish deputy chairman mr wing lam cheung independent director ms diana l taylor independent director mr kevin c conroy independent director ms jessica m bibliowicz independent director mr harry james wilson independent director mr olivier reza independent director mr daniel seth loeb independent director ms marsha e simms independent director log in  am edt july   marketstatecountryus new york open marketstatecountryuk london open marketstatecountryjp tokyo closed marketstatecountryus   marketstatecountryuk   market