mporary feel in terms of creativity it’s natural to compare the masterpieces of yesterday and today to come to the conclusion that they are products of the same philosophy in terms of the size of the jewels the same attention to the proportions of the stone and the same use of the most sophisticated working methods like the “en tremblant” technique carried out by the father and now the son to offer a bit of movement to the individual pieces that bring a jewel to life di maristella campi published     add comment  last on vogue vogue artsvittoria mentasti  dead seavittoria mentastis dead sea takes us to a place where the sky and the sea are onevogue artskristin prim and the provocateurs lettersa chat with kristin prim the founder of the provocateur the site that publishes letters written expressely by leading women addressing the whole female world vogueit presents you an exclusive preview of the letter written by dresden dolls amanda palmerstar newskanye west yeezy season  at the new york fashion week the new album and the controversy with taylor swiftduring the yeezy season  fashion show kanye west presented his new album the life of pablo heres everything you need to know and lets get ready to the fight with taylor swiftfashion eventsnew york fashion week all the eventsthe most exclusive parties at the new york fashion weekvoguistasnew york fashion week the street styleall the best street style spotted at new york fashion weekfocus on modelsmodels look the models style in new yorkfrom new york fashion week fall winter  notizie del giornofashion shows are changing burberry and all that’s new on the runwaysmenswear and womenswear collections will walk together and will be on sale right after the show these are the news from burberry but the evolution is generalized runway shows are changingcuriosità phillip lim the th anniversarythe documentary that celebrates  phillip lims tenth anniversarycuriositàsocial media for fashionthe latest social media initiatives dedicat